         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] (with clear) water, transparent</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] (then) man is scared (indeed) [TB] then (man is scared indeed)</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] the tenth ([verse] collection about faith) [TB] (the tenth [verse] collection) about faith</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] as long as the wise has not given up [his] desires</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] (one should) firmly (make an effort)</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
